---
title: Carbonara Style Bacon Linguine with sprinkled chives and dressed leaves
description: Carbonara is a classic Italian dish, the trademark of which is its creamy texture and the inclusion of smoky salty bacon bits. It's a recipe that doesn't shy away from being rich, which makes the peppery rocket a perfect side.
